  "title": "fix(show-more): should hide button when show more is not available",
  "body": "As noticed by @timkelty in #2160, showMore button should not be rendered\r\nif there are not enough items to display based on the limits. With the\r\nnew connector API, this means that we should add a new parameter to\r\nthe renderer to give the information that this button should be\r\ndisplayed.\r\n\r\nfixes #2160\r\n\r\nhttp://faithful-anger.surge.sh/?query=Canon%20-%20PowerShot%20SX720%20HS%2020.3-Megapixel%20Digital%20Camera%20-%20Red&idx=instant_search&p=0&dFR%5Bbrand%5D%5B0%5D=Canon&hierarchical%5BhierarchicalCategories.lvl0%5D%5B0%5D=Cameras%20%26%20Camcorders&nR%5Bpopularity%5D%5B%3E%3D%5D%5B0%5D=0&is_v=2\r\n\r\nCheck the menu widget and the collapsible refinement list.",
